<hr />

<p><strong>Idaho Power wants to use pollution credits to buy wind power.</strong> Extra sulfur dioxide allowances could be used to buy wind generators or other green power. Ken Dey in the <a href="http://www.idahostatesman.com/newsupdates/story/253651.html" target="blank">Statesman</a>.</p>

<p><strong>Abuse group has questions about Mtn. Home priest.</strong> Idaho church says it’s a personell matter and a lay review board found no evidece of sexual abuse of miors. But SNAP, a national support group for people abused by priests wants to know why he is on leave. Bill Roberts in the <a href="http://www.idahostatesman.com/235/story/253645.html">Statesman</a>.</p>

<p><strong>Why is Obama the only Democrat making a try in Idaho?</strong> Campaign aids say: because he can. Hoffman in <a href="http://www.boiseweekly.com/gyrobase/Content?oid=oid%3A309936">BW</a>.</p>

<p><strong>McCain and Obama at top of fundraising ticket in South-Central (Idaho).</strong> McCain tops Rudy and Mitt in Magic and Wood River valleys. Jared S. Hopkins in the <a href="http://www.magicvalley.com/articles/2008/01/03/news/top_story/127961.txt">Times-News.</a></p>

<p><strong>Christian group looking to move en masse to Gem Co.</strong> Leader was going to move to SC but he’s broke. Gem Co. officials have heard nothing. Liz Carey in the <a href="http://www.idahopress.com/?id=2850">IPT</a>.</p>

<p><strong>Ferguson reviews the governor’s first year.</strong> From secret swearing in ceremony that was fun to property tax freeze declarations. Dean Ferguson in the <a href="http://www.lmtribune.com/story/northwest/12964/">LMT</a>.</p>

<p><strong>Idaho Meth Project to launch.</strong> Anti-meth ad campaign will start Monday, to coincide with State of the State speech. Brad W. Gary in the <a href="http://www.lmtribune.com/story/northwest/12947/">LMT</a>.</p>

<p><strong>Coverage of a well-attended meeting on a proposed Payette Co. Nuke plant.</strong> Janet Monti in the <a href="http://www.messenger-index.com/?id=474">Messenger-Index</a> (partial story online).</p>
